			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				How I use this spell is have party at a safe pull area.  Then root mob A.  (which aggros mob B since it's nearby).  Bring mob B back to party.  Run back and cast atone twice on Mob A (which is still rooted far from the party).<BR>
<BR>
Viola.<BR>
<BR>
Root is resisted MUCH less than Pacify line of spells so I've been more successful using this technique versus Pacify, pull.  Let's face it as a cleric we can't have all the spells we want, mem'd.  Root and Atone are my mob control spells of choice.<BR>
<BR>
Tallor, 40th Cleric<BR>
White Wolf Brigade<BR>
Brell Serilis
				</font>
